provisions.content:
expressions shall have the meanings hereby respectively assigned to them, that is to say__
(a)        “affected area” means any area affected by an agricultural pest;
(b)        “agricultural pest” means a pest mentioned in the Schedule to this Ordinance;
(c)        “crops” include all agricultural or horticultural crops and all trees, bushes or
plants;
(d)        “Government” means the Government of West Pakistan;
(e)        “infested crop” means a crop affected by any agricultural pest;
(f)        “Inspector” means an officer appointed under this Ordinance to perform the
functions of an Inspector;
(g)        “occupier” means the person in actual possession of land and includes the
manager or managing agent or any other person authorised to represent the
occupier;
