(h)    “preventive measures” means measures prescribed by Government to eradicate
and to prevent the spread of any agricultural pest; and
(i)    “prescribed” means prescribed by rules made under this Ordinance.

(a)    the employment of such methods of cultivation as help the spread of agricultural
pests either generally or with respect to any particular crop;
(b)    the transport or sale of any infested crop.
